---
title: Brie-Stuffed Apples with Arugula, Baby Spinach and Balsamic Drizzle
description: Brie-stuffed apples are the perfect cold-weather comfort food! For a simple but luxurious side, we've adorned a crisp arugula and spinach salad with crunchy walnuts and drizzled it all with balsamic.
